28a463dfe909","tid":175744,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"睇到個公司又出新包嚇到叫左出黎，經理問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"4ce24c13d5ada885d775672f2a1b98eceb166c91","tid":175744,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"搵阿嬌代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade5805c0c091ff62ca66df2ccafa1eb56d90189","tid":175744,"uid":16332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"今次幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0d2eec61905a8e5829d3a4d5e3cfe1a7116f21","tid":175744,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲色素重要 食死人"},{"pid":"ccbc5d86da2965a52d0f369a64924da501933158","tid":175744,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲色素重<span style=\"color: red;\">到</span> 食死人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5b40e5fceeaea0678bf6f65bf9744811be6c0971","tid":175744,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"出日式包<br />\n點解唔出和牛漢堡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3e986c2a49d0c3c0134eab850ab747901eea0c","tid":175744,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"舊雞咪又係之前新包塊雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4cd88e7a6d276bf35a07433c01b34620d8e447","tid":175744,"uid":1314